(Iceweasel is required, because Tor Browser no longer supports visiting 127.0.0.1. Any other browser would work as well.)

Install web software.

<pre>
sudo apt-get install git apache2 php5-mysql php5 libapache2-mod-php5 mysql-client mysql-server iceweasel
</pre>

You will be asked for a mysql root password. Remember it.

Get our wiki images and content database backup.

<pre>
git clone --depth=1 https://github.com/WhonixBOT/WhonixWikiBackups.git
</pre>

Get and install the mediawiki web app.

<pre>
sudo su
cd /var/www
wget http://releases.wikimedia.org/mediawiki/1.22/mediawiki-1.22.3.tar.gz
tar -xvzf mediawiki-1.22.3.tar.gz
mv mediawiki-1.22.3 wiki
</pre>

Start iceweasel.

Setup mediawiki. Go to http://127.0.0.1/wiki/mw-config/index.php.

Use the following settings.

<pre>
Database name: wiki
Datebase password: what you remembered above
No more questions.
Otherwise use the defaults.
Name of wiki:
Whonix
</pre>

Download LocalSettings.php, safe as /home/user/LocalSettings.php.

<pre>
cd wiki
cp /home/user/LocalSettings.php /var/www/wiki/
php maintenance/importDump.php /home/user/WhonixWikiBackups/dumpContentCurrent.xml
php maintenance/update.php
php maintenance/importImages.php /home/user/WhonixWikiBackups/mediafiles/
</pre>

Go to http://127.0.0.1/wiki/index.php/Main_Page.

